<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mdui@1.0.1/dist/css/mdui.min.css" integrity="sha384-cLRrMq39HOZdvE0j6yBojO4+1PrHfB7a9l5qLcmRm/fiWXYY+CndJPmyu5FV/9Tw" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/forum.ico" type="image-x-icon">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.staticfile.org/twitter-bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.staticfile.org/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.staticfile.org/popper.js/1.15.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.staticfile.org/twitter-bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body class="mdui-theme-layout-dark">
    <h1>登录</h1>
    <form action="/api/check" method="post" id="loginForm" class="mdui-shadow-2">
        <input type="text" name="use" value="log" style="display: none;" readonly>
        <!-- <input type="text" name="id" placeholder="用户id" required> -->
        <div class="mdui-textfield mdui-textfield-floating-label">
            <label class="mdui-textfield-label">用户id</label>
            <input name="id" class="mdui-textfield-input" type="text" />
        </div>
        <!-- <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="密码" required> -->
        <div class="mdui-textfield mdui-textfield-floating-label">
            <label class="mdui-textfield-label">密码</label>
            <input name="password" class="mdui-textfield-input" type="password" />
        </div>
        <input type="submit" value="登录">
    </form>
    <p style="color: red;">目前仅支持使用用户id登录，所以请务必记住您的用户id！！</p>
    <a href="/users/reg">注册</a><br><a href="/home">返回</a>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mdui@1.0.1/dist/js/mdui.min.js" integrity="sha384-gCMZcshYKOGRX9r6wbDrvF+TcCCswSHFucUzUPwka+Gr+uHgjlYvkABr95TCOz3A" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>